{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Ignite Podcasting Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* A vibrant red */\n            --secondary-color: #f8bbd0; /* A softer pink */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #212121; /* Dark grey background */\n            --card-background: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n            border-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card img {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 3px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--brand-color));\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            color: #bbb;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                padding: 0 1rem;\n            }\n            section {\n                padding: 1.5rem;\n            }\n            .podcast-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Ignite Podcasting Network</h1>\n        <p>Sparking conversations, igniting ideas.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ignite Podcasting Network is a vibrant hub for creators and listeners alike. We are passionate about delivering engaging, diverse, and high-quality audio content that entertains, educates, and inspires. From true crime thrillers to insightful tech discussions, we've got a show for every ear.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"podcasts\">\n            <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/e53935/ffffff?text=TH\" alt=\"Podcast 1\">\n                    <h3>The History Buffs</h3>\n                    <p>Dive deep into the most fascinating events and figures from the past.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/f8bbd0/ffffff?text=SC\" alt=\"Podcast 2\">\n                    <h3>Sci-Fi Chronicles</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the future, one alien planet at a time. Interviews with authors and scientists.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/c62828/ffffff?text=CR\" alt=\"Podcast 3\">\n                    <h3>Crime Scene Confidential</h3>\n                    <p>Unraveling the mysteries of unsolved cases and forensic science.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/100/ef9a9a/ffffff?text=TK\" alt=\"Podcast 4\">\n                    <h3>Tech Knows</h3>\n                    <p>The latest in technology, gadgets, and the digital world.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"join\">\n            <h2>Join the Network</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Are you a podcaster looking for a supportive community and wider reach? Or a listener eager to discover new shows? We're building something special. Connect with us!</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"window.location.href='mailto:info@ignitepodcasts.com';\">Contact Us</button>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Ignite Podcasting Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Follow us on <a href=\"#\">Social Media</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}